text:
My phone auto-transcribes voicemails.
It made a choice.

“If you were Teresa…”
I was…until this voicemail.

Press 1 if you exist.
Press 2 if you’re also from Hell. 🔥😈

Regardless of my current existential status…
still available for VO work.
...in this realm and others. 🎙️🔥 https://t.co/4rCs3Jqf95
“let me transfer you to someone who can help you switch therapists” and it goes to voicemail. ok. not at all her fault though just funny as hell

@caitoz Mandy Sacher insanely hallucinated gunshots from harmless pocket-dial creaks/snoring in a dead-silent voicemail, then frantically sicced the cops on a disabled woman—unleashing hate-crime hell over delusional paranoia. Utterly deranged, vindictive hysteria.
A voiceless voicemail made her nervous because there were noises like gunshots….fucking Hell. https://t.co/yqbOzg77Zc
